WEBVTT

1
00:00:07.957 --> 00:00:12.512
<i>GODFREY [ON TV]: So the Justice League
finally provided scanners...</i>

2
00:00:12.556 --> 00:00:14.593
<i>to every government on Earth...</i>

3
00:00:14.759 --> 00:00:17.933
<i>to root out those
filthy little aliens...</i>

4
00:00:18.095 --> 00:00:21.042
<i>posing as real human beings.</i>

5
00:00:21.198 --> 00:00:27.513
<i>But you have to wonder. how were they
able to whip up this tech so fast?</i>

6
00:00:27.671 --> 00:00:32.450
<i>Or more accurately.
how long have they been keeping it from us?</i>

7
00:00:32.610 --> 00:00:36.820
<i>Oh. sure. they offer it up
like a gift from the gods.</i>

8
00:00:36.981 --> 00:00:39.621
Sit anywhere. kids.

9
00:00:40.251 --> 00:00:41.559
[GASPS]

10
00:01:10.681 --> 00:01:12.024
[GRUNTS]

11
00:01:15.352 --> 00:01:19.801
There's only one Bibbo.
and don't you forget it.

12
00:01:24.929 --> 00:01:26.931
[GROWLING]

13
00:01:40.811 --> 00:01:45.157
Huh. Boy.
That practically singed my eyebrows off.

14
00:01:45.316 --> 00:01:48.092
Yeah. Practically.

15
00:01:48.252 --> 00:01:51.631
- Uh. you got a little so...
- Blue. scan for it!

16
00:01:51.789 --> 00:01:54.599
Right. right. Scanning.

17
00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:59.464
Sorry. Nothing. He's gone.

18
00:01:59.630 --> 00:02:04.636
No. it would not have been preferable
to vaporize him back at the diner.

19
00:02:19.216 --> 00:02:20.422
<i>BLACK MANTA:
Welcome aboard.</i>

20
00:02:23.287 --> 00:02:24.732
Dive.

21
00:02:34.785 --> 00:02:39.785
<i>♪ <font color="#ff0000">Young Justice</font>: "<font color="#ffd700">Alienated</font>" ♪</i>
Season 2 Episode 3

22
00:02:48.946 --> 00:02:51.358
<i>MAN: Sir?
We've received the Rannian signal.</i>

23
00:02:53.450 --> 00:02:55.259
They're arriving now.

24
00:02:55.920 --> 00:02:59.561
<i>COMPUTER:
Recognized: Adam Strange. A-1-1.</i>

25
00:02:59.723 --> 00:03:02.761
<i>Miss Martian. B-0-5.</i>

26
00:03:02.927 --> 00:03:08.206
<i>Superboy. B-0-4.
Beast Boy. B-1-9.</i>

27
00:03:08.365 --> 00:03:09.565
<i>BEAST BOY:
Nightwing!</i>

28
00:03:09.600 --> 00:03:12.103
Check out my super-cool alien souvenir.

29
00:03:12.269 --> 00:03:14.977
<i>MISS MARTIAN: Gar. Business first.
BEAST BOY: Noted.</i>

30
00:03:15.139 --> 00:03:16.743
Zeta Squad. report.

31
00:03:16.907 --> 00:03:20.912
Our mission to neutralize the Krolotean's
Zeta-Platforms on Rann was a success.

32
00:03:21.078 --> 00:03:23.354
I've brought back specs
to create a Zeta-Shield...

33
00:03:23.514 --> 00:03:26.586
to prevent any more aliens
from beaming to Earth from off-world.

34
00:03:26.750 --> 00:03:29.424
How will that affect
our own Zeta-capabilities?

35
00:03:29.587 --> 00:03:33.399
It won't. The Shield will activate at an
altitude above the Watchtower's orbit.

36
00:03:33.557 --> 00:03:35.730
League Zeta-Tubes
will still function normally.

37
00:03:35.893 --> 00:03:39.067
Tell them about Rimbor.
Tell them about the 16 hours.

38
00:03:42.166 --> 00:03:45.170
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
It may be easier to show you.</i>

39
00:03:48.205 --> 00:03:51.675
<i>I successfully interrogated
a Krolotean general on Rann...</i>

40
00:03:51.842 --> 00:03:54.823
<i>who had paid off a member
of the Rannian Science Command...</i>

41
00:03:54.979 --> 00:03:59.485
<i>to allow the Kroloteans to land
a secret base in the Rannian jungle.</i>

42
00:03:59.650 --> 00:04:03.325
<i>Once there. the Kroloteans stole
Zeta-Platform technology...</i>

43
00:04:03.487 --> 00:04:06.297
<i>from Adam Strange's friend. Sardath.</i>

44
00:04:06.457 --> 00:04:08.528
<i>They landed another ship
in New Orleans...</i>

45
00:04:08.692 --> 00:04:12.868
<i>and used the Zeta-Platforms to beam
a few hundred Kroloteans to Earth.</i>

46
00:04:13.030 --> 00:04:15.601
<i>They built more platforms.
brought in more Kroloteans...</i>

47
00:04:15.766 --> 00:04:18.838
<i>and began
abducting and replacing humans.</i>

48
00:04:19.003 --> 00:04:23.281
Perhaps as part of an invasion strategy.
though that's still unclear.

49
00:04:23.440 --> 00:04:24.640
But why Earth?

50
00:04:24.742 --> 00:04:27.780
And what does any of this have to do
with the 16 hours?

51
00:04:27.945 --> 00:04:30.391
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
Well. as you know...</i>

52
00:04:30.547 --> 00:04:35.792
<i>five years ago. Vandal Savage placed
the entire League under his control.</i>

53
00:04:35.953 --> 00:04:39.127
<i>Six leaguers:
Superman. Batman. Wonder Woman...</i>

54
00:04:39.290 --> 00:04:42.169
<i>Martian Manhunter. Green Lantern
and Hawkwoman...</i>

55
00:04:42.326 --> 00:04:45.398
<i>went missing
for a full 16 hours.</i>

56
00:04:46.330 --> 00:04:49.800
<i>It turns out you were teleported
to a planet called Rimbor...</i>

57
00:04:49.967 --> 00:04:52.743
<i>where you spent 16 hours on a rampage...</i>

58
00:04:53.137 --> 00:04:55.526
<i>attacking everyone
and everything in sight...</i>

59
00:04:55.565 --> 00:04:58.089
<i>and announcing in several
alien languages</i>

60
00:04:58.115 --> 00:05:00.344
<i>that you were the Justice League
from Earth...</i>

61
00:05:00.377 --> 00:05:02.721
<i>and that the rest of the galaxy
should beware.</i>

62
00:05:03.714 --> 00:05:05.489
That's why the Kroloteans came.

63
00:05:05.649 --> 00:05:08.186
The League itself
brought Earth to their attention.

64
00:05:09.186 --> 00:05:13.896
I don't know what to say.
I have no memories of this. None.

65
00:05:14.058 --> 00:05:17.904
Don't blame yourself.
Blame Savage and his Light.

66
00:05:18.062 --> 00:05:23.307
But John. how is it that you haven't heard
about this intergalactic incident'?

67
00:05:23.467 --> 00:05:26.546
No clue. Rimbor's not a planet
in my sector.

68
00:05:26.581 --> 00:05:28.348
But I'll head to Oa
immediately.

69
00:05:28.356 --> 00:05:31.584
to consult with the Guardians of
the Universe and Green Lantern Corps.

70
00:05:31.742 --> 00:05:34.723
We'll get to the bottom of this. Cap.
I promise.

71
00:05:34.878 --> 00:05:36.078
In the meantime...

72
00:05:36.180 --> 00:05:39.491
we still have a Krolotean invasion force
to track down on Earth.

73
00:05:39.650 --> 00:05:42.631
You did good work on Rann.
Now we need you...

74
00:05:43.187 --> 00:05:45.531
<i>at the Hall of Justice.</i>

75
00:05:48.992 --> 00:05:50.994
[CHILDREN CHATTERING]

76
00:06:01.138 --> 00:06:05.587
<i>CATHERINE: And finally. we have
the four surviving host bodies...</i>

77
00:06:05.743 --> 00:06:10.852
mused by a race of alien energy beings
known as the Appelaxians...

78
00:06:11.014 --> 00:06:14.018
who attempted to conquer the Earth.

79
00:06:14.551 --> 00:06:19.500
Of course. the attack also brought together
Earth's mightiest heroes...

80
00:06:19.656 --> 00:06:22.227
to form the Justice League.

81
00:06:22.393 --> 00:06:25.897
G. Gordon Godfrey says the League
is working with the aliens.

82
00:06:26.063 --> 00:06:29.670
Ahem. This way to the viewing gallery.

83
00:06:31.635 --> 00:06:35.173
<i>MISS MARTIAN: You didn't have to come along.
SUPERBOY: I think I did.</i>

84
00:06:35.324 --> 00:06:38.430
This is the Krolotean
captured by Lagoon Boy. Robin and Beetle?

85
00:06:38.654 --> 00:06:41.157
Your uncle has been interrogating him
for days...

86
00:06:41.323 --> 00:06:44.736
but simply achieving psychic translation
has proven difficult.

87
00:06:44.893 --> 00:06:48.431
In the meantime. the League and the Team
have hunted the Kroloteans...

88
00:06:48.597 --> 00:06:50.634
that had been masquerading
as humans.

89
00:06:50.799 --> 00:06:56.215
But all have escaped capture. despite the fact
that we destroyed their Zeta-Platforms here...

90
00:06:56.371 --> 00:07:00.342
and on Rann. and that they.
apparently. destroyed their own ship.

91
00:07:00.509 --> 00:07:02.511
[GROWLING]

92
00:07:04.246 --> 00:07:07.921
<i>After your success on Rann. Captain Atom
thought you might be of some assis...</i>

93
00:07:08.083 --> 00:07:10.495
The Kroloteans have an emergency
rendezvous point...

94
00:07:10.652 --> 00:07:14.930
and have standing orders
in case of discovery to evacuate there.

95
00:07:15.090 --> 00:07:16.933
A base inside a volcano...

96
00:07:17.426 --> 00:07:19.872
<i>on Malina Island.</i>

97
00:07:48.657 --> 00:07:50.659
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

98
00:07:55.497 --> 00:07:58.222
<i>BLACK MANTA 1: We have arrived
with the final shipment of Kroloteans.</i>

99
00:07:58.233 --> 00:08:00.975
<i>BLACK MANTA 2 [ON SCREEN]:
Congratulations. my son.</i>

100
00:08:01.670 --> 00:08:05.379
Thank you. Father.
Initiating Phase Two.

101
00:08:13.887 --> 00:08:17.630
<i>BATMAN: Remember. this is
primarily a recon mission.</i>

102
00:08:17.791 --> 00:08:21.889
We wanna discover all we can
about the Kroloteans' invasion strategy...

103
00:08:21.919 --> 00:08:26.129
before we shut them down and deliver
them to the Green Lantern Corps.

104
00:08:26.366 --> 00:08:29.006
<i>NIGHTWING:
Approaching drop-zone Beta.</i>

105
00:08:44.051 --> 00:08:45.291
[IN ATLANTEAN]

106
00:08:45.719 --> 00:08:46.959
[IN ATLANTEAN]

107
00:08:55.596 --> 00:08:57.507
Drop-zone Gamma.

108
00:09:02.135 --> 00:09:03.842
[CRASHING]

109
00:09:23.056 --> 00:09:25.002
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

110
00:09:25.192 --> 00:09:26.967
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

111
00:09:27.461 --> 00:09:28.997
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

112
00:09:31.531 --> 00:09:33.533
[KROLOTEANS GROWLING]

113
00:09:47.214 --> 00:09:50.320
- All sectors. report status.
<i>MAN 1 [OVER RADIO]: Sector One. secure.</i>

114
00:09:50.484 --> 00:09:52.225
<i>MAN 2:
Sector Two. secure.</i>

115
00:09:52.386 --> 00:09:53.660
<i>MAN 3:
Sector Four. secure.</i>

116
00:09:54.221 --> 00:09:56.792
Sector Three. report status.

117
00:09:58.358 --> 00:10:00.304
<i>[OVER RADIO]
Sector Three. report.</i>

118
00:10:23.984 --> 00:10:28.592
<i>AQUALAD [IN BLACK MANTA'S VOICE]:
Intruders. Upper Level. And in the water.</i>

119
00:10:31.458 --> 00:10:33.199
<i>GUARD:
There.</i>

120
00:10:34.594 --> 00:10:35.868
[GRUNTING]

121
00:10:44.504 --> 00:10:45.704
[GRUNTS]

122
00:11:01.788 --> 00:11:03.426
[YELLS]

123
00:11:26.113 --> 00:11:28.753
Batgirl. Maneuver Seven.

124
00:11:39.126 --> 00:11:41.128
[BEEPING]

125
00:11:42.829 --> 00:11:44.831
[GUARDS YELLING]

126
00:11:57.744 --> 00:12:01.580
<i>AQUALAD: Manta to Partner. The base
has been infiltrated. Abort operation.</i>

127
00:12:01.632 --> 00:12:04.636
<i>MAN [OVER RADIO]: Partner to Manta.
The device is already primed.</i>

128
00:12:04.684 --> 00:12:07.654
<i>You have five minutes.
Get your men out.</i>

129
00:12:07.687 --> 00:12:12.830
<i>- The bomb will take care of the rest.</i>
- Perfect.

130
00:12:19.312 --> 00:12:23.490
<i>AQUALAD: Manta to all troopers. Endgame
enabled. Strategic retreat to Manta Flyer.</i>

131
00:12:23.520 --> 00:12:25.932
You have four minutes.

132
00:12:30.089 --> 00:12:31.569
<i>NIGHTWING:
Nightwing to Delta Squad.</i>

133
00:12:31.601 --> 00:12:33.877
Enemy is attempting escape.
Request backup.

134
00:12:33.960 --> 00:12:35.962
[YELLING]

135
00:12:45.805 --> 00:12:49.184
- [IN ENGLISH] Nice aim.
- X-ray vision. I cheat.

136
00:12:49.342 --> 00:12:51.379
Superman. triple combo over here.

137
00:13:00.519 --> 00:13:03.398
Quadruple. Nice.

138
00:13:07.760 --> 00:13:08.966
[SCREECHES]

139
00:13:19.672 --> 00:13:22.414
That was amazing.
You just. you just...

140
00:13:22.575 --> 00:13:25.283
whoosh and then
and then. and then. barn!

141
00:13:26.345 --> 00:13:28.985
Little less fan girl.
little more Wonder Girl.

142
00:13:29.315 --> 00:13:31.454
Right. Sorry.

143
00:13:51.070 --> 00:13:52.981
<i>AQUALAD:
Three minutes to departure.</i>

144
00:13:53.139 --> 00:13:55.141
[LAGOON BOY YELLS]

145
00:14:06.746 --> 00:14:09.784
I had not believed Nightwing
until this moment.

146
00:14:10.716 --> 00:14:14.027
- You did not want to believe!
- None of us wanted to believe this!

147
00:14:14.186 --> 00:14:17.565
- How could you betray us?
- You dare question me?

148
00:14:17.723 --> 00:14:20.033
After all of you let Tula die!

149
00:14:20.926 --> 00:14:24.100
Kaldur. that was a mission.
Aquagirl knew the risks!

150
00:14:24.163 --> 00:14:26.453
- No one wanted her to...
<i>LAGOON BOY [IN ENGLISH]: Neptune's beard!</i>

151
00:14:26.465 --> 00:14:27.944
Don't cuddle this traitor.

152
00:14:28.100 --> 00:14:30.910
He has joined forces
with our King's greatest enemy.

153
00:14:31.070 --> 00:14:34.483
Do you mean the King who hid from me
the true identity of my father?

154
00:14:34.640 --> 00:14:37.086
That was my error in judgment.
Kaldur'ahm.

155
00:14:37.243 --> 00:14:39.086
No one else need suffer for it.

156
00:14:39.245 --> 00:14:41.851
All will suffer if Black Manta demands it.

157
00:14:42.014 --> 00:14:44.722
Blood is thicker than seawater.

158
00:14:55.327 --> 00:14:56.965
<i>NIGHTWING:
Kaldur?</i>

159
00:14:58.264 --> 00:15:01.973
Just you and me. old friend?
<i>SUPERBOY: No!</i>

160
00:15:02.134 --> 00:15:05.240
It's a regular reunion special.

161
00:15:05.771 --> 00:15:08.251
Fine. You can take me down...

162
00:15:08.407 --> 00:15:11.183
or you can save everyone
from this bomb.

163
00:15:12.411 --> 00:15:15.153
I am told the yield is quite impressive.

164
00:15:15.314 --> 00:15:16.514
[YELLS]

165
00:15:17.183 --> 00:15:18.856
[GROANING]

166
00:15:19.018 --> 00:15:20.793
You have two minutes.

167
00:15:31.197 --> 00:15:34.201
- They're getting away!
- We'll stop them!

168
00:15:34.366 --> 00:15:36.403
<i>NIGHTWING: Negative.
We have a bomb down here.</i>

169
00:15:36.569 --> 00:15:39.444
- Alien tech. I cannot disarm it.
- I'll get it out.

170
00:15:39.505 --> 00:15:42.611
No! Might have
pressure or motion sensors.

171
00:15:42.775 --> 00:15:45.779
All Squads. evacuate to Bio-Ship. Now.

172
00:15:54.987 --> 00:15:57.797
You heard Nightwing. Move.

173
00:16:04.897 --> 00:16:06.843
Listen! Listen to me!

174
00:16:07.466 --> 00:16:09.468
[IN ALIEN LANGUAGE]

175
00:16:16.075 --> 00:16:20.046
- Neptune's beard.
- [IN MISS MARTIAN'S VOICE] Hello. Megan.

176
00:16:20.212 --> 00:16:22.214
Knew we forgot something.

177
00:16:22.381 --> 00:16:25.919
- Well done. Alpha Squad.
- Find a seat. It's time to go.

178
00:16:26.085 --> 00:16:28.190
Wait. Where's Superman?

179
00:16:28.354 --> 00:16:30.818
Listen! I am not trying to hurt you!

180
00:16:30.873 --> 00:16:33.461
A bomb is set to explode
beneath this base.

181
00:16:33.523 --> 00:16:36.026
There are too many of you
to carry individually...

182
00:16:36.192 --> 00:16:40.299
but if you board your ship.
I will fly you all to safety.

183
00:16:42.365 --> 00:16:44.003
Please!

184
00:16:51.040 --> 00:16:53.042
[BEEPING]

185
00:17:04.190 --> 00:17:06.170
[ALL GRUNTING]

186
00:17:07.360 --> 00:17:08.964
<i>MISS MARTIAN:
Come on. old girl.</i>

187
00:17:40.678 --> 00:17:43.659
He's breathing. Pulse is strong.
He'll be all right.

188
00:17:43.815 --> 00:17:47.991
He didn't save the Kroloteans.
He won't be all right with that.

189
00:17:48.092 --> 00:17:49.292
What just happened?

190
00:17:49.393 --> 00:17:51.930
The Kroloteans were clearly trying
to build a new ship.

191
00:17:52.096 --> 00:17:53.575
They had to. Angelfish.

192
00:17:53.731 --> 00:17:57.611
It was their only way to leave Earth without
their Zeta-Platforms or original ship.

193
00:17:57.724 --> 00:18:01.695
<i>WONDER GIRL: But was Aqualad helping them
escape or luring them into a trap?</i>

194
00:18:02.395 --> 00:18:06.673
The bomb was of alien origin. yet the
Kroloteans clearly knew nothing about it.

195
00:18:06.833 --> 00:18:08.369
So where did it come from?

196
00:18:08.489 --> 00:18:13.404
I have the feeling it may be up to you
and your Team to find out.

197
00:18:23.793 --> 00:18:27.070
- Father.
- Congratulations. son. You did well.

198
00:18:27.700 --> 00:18:31.045
I don't suppose Aquaman
died in the explosion.

199
00:18:31.537 --> 00:18:33.175
Unlikely.

200
00:18:33.539 --> 00:18:34.739
[BLACK MANTA SIGHS]

201
00:18:34.741 --> 00:18:35.941
Pity.

202
00:18:35.942 --> 00:18:37.785
[ALARM WAILING]

203
00:18:37.944 --> 00:18:40.288
If you'll excuse me...

204
00:18:47.920 --> 00:18:50.127
<i>Good morning. Black Manta.</i>

205
00:18:50.289 --> 00:18:56.103
<i>The Krolotean's competitor. our new Partner.
is quite pleased with your efforts.</i>

206
00:18:56.262 --> 00:18:58.105
<i>And so is the Light.</i>

207
00:18:58.264 --> 00:19:00.266
<i>All agree we made the right choice...</i>

208
00:19:00.433 --> 00:19:05.212
<i>asking you to replace
poor. disgraced Ocean Master.</i>

209
00:19:05.401 --> 00:19:10.407
<i>You are officially one with the Light.</i>

210
00:19:22.585 --> 00:19:26.032
- I wish I could go with.
- I doubt your mother would approve.

211
00:19:26.189 --> 00:19:29.568
And only the six of us who stand accused
need take this odyssey...

212
00:19:29.726 --> 00:19:34.471
though Hawkman insists on accompanying his
spouse and Icon will act as our advocate...

213
00:19:34.630 --> 00:19:38.601
for it seems he is familiar
with intergalactic trial law.

214
00:19:38.768 --> 00:19:40.270
You're sure this is necessary?

215
00:19:40.436 --> 00:19:42.712
The Guardians of the Universe
seem to think so.

216
00:19:42.872 --> 00:19:46.820
They've sent Hal and Guy ahead to make
sure the so-called High Court of Rimbor...

217
00:19:46.976 --> 00:19:51.789
will know we come in peace.
And know we expect a fair trial.

218
00:19:52.014 --> 00:19:53.220
How long will you be gone?

219
00:19:53.382 --> 00:19:55.726
However long it takes
to clear our names. Kon-El.

220
00:19:55.885 --> 00:19:58.126
But we will be back. little brother.

221
00:19:58.888 --> 00:20:01.892
- I'll miss you.
- And I. you. M'gann.

222
00:20:02.058 --> 00:20:06.473
Oh. Perhaps you could water the plants
in my apartment while I am gone.

223
